## Project Setup and Tooling

Canonical reference: [package.json](mdc:package.json)

### Scripts

-   `dev`: Vite dev server
-   `build`: TypeScript build (project refs) then Vite build
-   `lint`: ESLint across repo
-   `preview`: Vite preview

### Runtime dependencies

-   React 19 + ReactDOM 19
-   three + @types/three
-   @react-three/fiber, @react-three/drei, @react-three/rapier
-   State/UI helpers: jotai, leva

### Dev dependencies

-   Vite 7 + @vitejs/plugin-react
-   TypeScript ~5.8
-   ESLint 9 + react-refresh + react-hooks
-   types for React / ReactDOM

### Conventions

-   Use TypeScript with module type.
-   Keep versions in sync with `package.json`.
-   Rendering via R3F; physics via Rapier; models via GLTF.
